    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'mint condition.' This garage-kept masterpiece retains its original showroom luster, protected by a professional ceramic coating with absolutely zero stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolster wear and still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at the dealership, with a complete folder of maintenance records available for inspection. From the curb-rash-free alloy wheels to the spotless, dust-free engine bay, this car looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. A rare find for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection without compromise.",
